Files: local-vendor-liboqs
Copyright: 2016-2024 Open Quantum Safe project contributors
License: MIT
Comment:
 Local non-archive builds may statically link liboqs from the YUME
 ../vendor/linux-x86_64 staging directory to enable ML-KEM-768 before a
 Debian liboqs package is available. Debian archive builds should replace
 this with a normal liboqs-dev Build-Depends and dynamic/shared-library
 dependency.

